    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">You supercool the nearby air, forming a cloud of dancing ice crystals in an emanation around you. A creature other than you that enters the area or ends its turn within the area takes 2d6 cold damage. A creature can take this damage only once per turn. The crystals scatter and refract light; if a light effect enters diamond dust&rsquo;s area, any creatures that effect goes on to affect gain a +2 status bonus to AC and saves against it. While the spell persists, you can activate or deactivate this aura by using a single action, which has the</span> <span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">concentrate</span> <span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">trait. You can Dismiss this spell.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> The damage increases by 1d6.&nbsp;</p>",
